Package com.gcu.agms.repository

Interface MaintenanceRecordRepository

All Known Implementing Classes:
JdbcMaintenanceRecordRepository
public interface MaintenanceRecordRepository
Repository interface for maintenance record data access operations. Defines methods for performing CRUD operations and specific queries related to maintenance records.

      MaintenanceRecord save(MaintenanceRecord record)

      Returns:
